@startuml
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam shadowing false

box "Client Application" #f9f9f9
    participant "HCS" as Client
end box

box "Integration Services" #e1f5fe
    participant "FHIR API" as FHIR
    participant "MagicLink" as MagicLink
    participant "CMS" as CMS
end box

box "External" #f1f8e9
    actor "Patient" as Patient
end box

autonumber "<b>[00]"

== 1. CarePlan Creation & Magic Link ==

Client -> FHIR: POST CarePlan
return 201 Created (CarePlan ID)

Client -> MagicLink: Generate Magic Link (inc. CarePlan ID)
return 201 URL/Token

== 2. Communication Request ==

Client -> FHIR: << Bundle >>\nPOST CommunicationRequest\nPUT CarePlan
note right: CarePlan update includes\nref to CommunicationRequest
return 200 OK (BundleResponse)

== 3. Patient Notification ==

FHIR -> CMS: CommunicationRequest Notification
CMS -> Patient: Send SMS/Email

CMS -> FHIR: << Bundle >>\nPOST Communication\nPUT CarePlan
note right: Update CarePlan with\nref to Communication
return 200 OK (BundleResponse)

CMS -> FHIR: PUT CommunicationRequest (status=completed)
return 200 Updated

== 4. Patient Response ==

... Patient follows Magic Link ...

Patient -> MagicLink: Submits Questionnaire
MagicLink -> FHIR: << Bundle >>\nPOST QuestionnaireResponse\nPUT CarePlan
note right: Update CarePlan with\nref to QuestionnaireResponse
return 200 OK (BundleResponse)

== 5. Client Retrieval ==

Client -> FHIR: GET CarePlan?_id=[ID]\n&_include=CarePlan:activity:reference\n&_include=CarePlan:activity:outcomeReference\n&_include=CarePlan:activity:detail:instantiatesCanonical
note right
  **Includes:**
  * CommunicationRequest (reference)
  * QuestionnaireResponse (outcomeReference)
  * Communication (outcomeReference)
  * Questionnaire (instantiatesCanonical)
end note

return 200 OK (Bundle: SearchSet)
note left
  Contains CarePlan + 
  all linked resources 
  in a single response.
end note



@enduml